{"tid":716951,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"趁住夜晚 我想放一放負","createTime":"2018-06-25T16:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-26T01:25:34.000Z","uid":80982,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"f45e46e8e7e999c8fe3a7512f34ed78b355b9bff","tid":716951,"uid":80982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:33:29.000Z","msg":"我覺得自己愈來愈有問題 但係又改變唔到 好辛苦<br />\n好似唔想再受到傷害 漸漸收埋自己 <br />\n係以前既朋友堆面前 變得好陌生 變得好假 要自己戴住面具去相處<br />\n對人失去左信任 更加失去自信 <br />\n係咪人生低潮既時候只可以一個面對 戴住面具先可以生存"},{"pid":"776ef65f27079bf95190595942cc0f2faf2ed839","tid":716951,"uid":80982,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:36:48.000Z","msg":"我係人 我都有情緒 我都會唔開心架<br />\n我都想有人可以鼓勵我呀 我都想有熟既朋友可以講心事 <br />\n點解呀 我做錯咩呀"},{"pid":"c96b419c2a631938ae5a7f00363044c00113e32e","tid":716951,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4020a3d8ebb881dc668ac75473dee81bdd361187","tid":716951,"uid":80982,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c96b419c2a631938ae5a7f00363044c00113e32e","tid":716951,"uid":187076,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:38:52.000Z","msg":"加油<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:41:20.000Z","msg":"多謝你 仲以為有人屌我男人老狗冇撚用"},{"pid":"681e598a6bb1df9ee1a6e7f4bfb1ea64d8b47392","tid":716951,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:44:58.000Z","msg":"係"},{"pid":"33fb0dad6f999b2c9fe4e4716b63a61285b3dc1c","tid":716951,"uid":140798,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:46:27.000Z","msg":"都係 到最後都係靠自己"},{"pid":"56424f4308ee06591ee5e013483c47cf09fc559b","tid":716951,"uid":80353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T16:49:58.000Z","msg":"或者，每個人都會經歷呢個階段，唔需要覺得自己特別有問題。<br />\n <br />\n聽下呢首 <a href=\"https://youtu.be/T9V45Ih